.SH SYNOPSIS
\f[B]Note:\f[R] This feature is available in Web Workers.
.PP
The \f[B]\f[CB]WebGL2RenderingContext.bindBufferBase()\f[B]\f[R] method
of the WebGL 2 API binds a given \f[CR]WebGLBuffer\f[R] to a given
binding point (\f[CR]target\f[R]) at a given \f[CR]index\f[R].
.SH SYNTAX
.IP
.EX
bindBufferBase(target, index, buffer)
.EE
.SS Parameters
.TP
\f[B]target\f[R]
A \f[CR]GLenum\f[R] specifying the target for the bind operation.
Possible values:
.RS
.IP \(bu 2
\f[CR]gl.TRANSFORM_FEEDBACK_BUFFER\f[R]
.IP \(bu 2
\f[CR]gl.UNIFORM_BUFFER\f[R]
.RE
