\f[B]index\f[R]
A \f[CR]GLuint\f[R] specifying the index of the \f[CR]target\f[R].
.TP
\f[B]buffer\f[R]
A \f[CR]WebGLBuffer\f[R] which to bind to the binding point
(\f[CR]target\f[R]).
.SS Return value
None (\f[CR]undefined\f[R]).
